## 🛠️ Comandos de Setup para Mariam

### **Paso 1: Instalar dependencias**
```bash
npm install axios
```

### **Paso 2: Crear estructura de carpetas**
```bash
# Las carpetas ya existen, solo crear archivos
touch src/models/Task.model.js
touch src/models/Comment.model.js
touch src/controllers/task.controller.js
touch src/controllers/comment.controller.js
touch src/controllers/ai.controller.js
touch src/routes/task.routes.js
touch src/routes/comment.routes.js
touch src/routes/ai.routes.js
touch src/validators/task.validator.js
touch src/validators/comment.validator.js
touch src/validators/ai.validator.js
touch scripts/test-deepseek.js
```

### **Paso 3: Configurar DeepSeek**
```bash
# Ir a https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
# Obtener API key gratis
echo "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here" >> .env
```

### **Paso 4: Actualizar server.js**
```javascript
// Agregar estas líneas en server.js:
app.use('/api/tasks', require('./src/routes/task.routes'));
app.use('/api/comments', require('./src/routes/comment.routes'));
app.use('/api/ai', require('./src/routes/ai.routes'));
```

### **Paso 5: Probar configuración**
```bash
npm run test-deepseek
```

