## 🚀 Endpoints que Mariam implementará

### **📋 TAREAS (8 endpoints)**
```
GET    /api/tasks/projects/:projectId/tasks     # Listar tareas del proyecto
POST   /api/tasks/projects/:projectId/tasks     # Crear tarea
GET    /api/tasks/my-tasks                      # Mis tareas asignadas
GET    /api/tasks/:id                           # Ver tarea específica
PUT    /api/tasks/:id                           # Actualizar tarea
DELETE /api/tasks/:id                           # Eliminar tarea
PUT    /api/tasks/:id/status                    # Cambiar estado
PUT    /api/tasks/:id/assign                    # Asignar usuario
```

### **💬 COMENTARIOS (4 endpoints)**
```
GET    /api/comments/projects/:id/comments      # Listar comentarios
POST   /api/comments/projects/:id/comments      # Crear comentario
PUT    /api/comments/:id                        # Editar comentario
DELETE /api/comments/:id                        # Eliminar comentario
```

### **🤖 IA CON DEEPSEEK (5 endpoints)**
```
POST   /api/ai/generate-tasks                   # Generar tareas automáticamente
POST   /api/ai/analyze-project                  # Analizar salud del proyecto
POST   /api/ai/estimate-time                    # Estimar tiempo de tarea
POST   /api/ai/generate-summary                 # Resumen ejecutivo
POST   /api/ai/suggest-improvements             # Sugerir mejoras
```

### **📊 TOTAL: 17 endpoints funcionales**

